---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="BiohackMaps was built by biohackers for biohackers — the story behind the world's most complete directory of biohacking venues."
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h1>We built the map<br />we wished existed</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">A directory born out of frustration — and a cold plunge obsession.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-grid">
        <div class="story-text">
          <p class="lead">
            It started the same way it probably started for you. I was trying to find a cold plunge near me, and ended up deep in Reddit threads, dead links, and Google Maps reviews from 2019. It was painful.
          </p>
          <p>
            So I built a spreadsheet. Then a database. Then this. BiohackMaps is the directory I wanted — one place to find every infrared sauna, cryotherapy chamber, float tank, red-light therapy studio, and TRT clinic near you, wherever you are in the world.
          </p>
          <p>
            There's no VC money behind this. No growth-hacking team. Just a founder who takes cold plunges seriously and thinks more people should have easy access to these tools.
          </p>
          <p>
            We're currently tracking <strong>775+ venues</strong> across <strong>35+ cities</strong>, and we add new ones every week. If your favorite spot isn't listed yet, <a href="/contact/">tell us</a> — we'll get it on the map.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="story-aside">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">775+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Venues tracked</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">35+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Cities covered</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">6</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Modalities indexed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">Free</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Always, for searchers</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission">
        <p class="eyebrow">What We Believe</p>
        <h2>Biohacking should be accessible</h2>
        <p>
          The best recovery tools used to be locked inside elite sports facilities or expensive spas. That's changing fast — and BiohackMaps exists to help people find these services before they give up and go home.
        </p>
        <p>
          We don't take commissions on bookings. We don't sell your search data. We just want you to find the right venue, quickly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="modalities">
        <p class="eyebrow">What We Track</p>
        <h2>Every major modality, one directory</h2>
        <div class="modality-grid">
          <div class="modality-item">
            <span class="modality-icon">🔥</span>
            <h3>Infrared Sauna</h3>
            <p>Deep heat therapy for recovery, detox, and relaxation</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modality-item">
            <span class="modality-icon">🧊</span>
            <h3>Cryotherapy</h3>
            <p>Whole-body cold exposure for inflammation and performance</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modality-item">
            <span class="modality-icon">🌊</span>
            <h3>Float Tanks</h3>
            <p>Sensory deprivation for deep rest and mental clarity</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modality-item">
            <span class="modality-icon">💡</span>
            <h3>Red Light Therapy</h3>
            <p>Photobiomodulation for skin, recovery, and energy</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modality-item">
            <span class="modality-icon">🥶</span>
            <h3>Cold Plunge</h3>
            <p>Ice bath immersion for the brave and the obsessed</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modality-item">
            <span class="modality-icon">💉</span>
            <h3>TRT Clinics</h3>
            <p>Testosterone replacement therapy and hormone optimisation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Got a venue to add?</h2>
        <p>If you own a biohacking venue or know one that should be on the map, we want to hear from you.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/for-business/" class="button">List Your Venue</a>
          <a href="/contact/" class="button button-outline">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(249,115,22,0.08) 0%, transparent 65%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 56px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .section-dark {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Story */
  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-text .lead {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .story-text p strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .story-text a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .story-aside {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* Mission */
  .mission {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .mission h2 {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .mission p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* Modalities */
  .modalities {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .modalities h2 {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .modality-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .modality-item {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .modality-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .modality-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .modality-item h3 {
    font-size: 17px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .modality-item p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .section-cta {
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(6,182,212,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cta-block {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-block h2 {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cta-block p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--black);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .button:hover {
    background: var(--accent2);
  }

  .button-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .button-outline:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .story-aside {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 38px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .modality-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .story-aside {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
    }

    .modality-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .story-aside {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
